LCScan installation instructions for Linux operation system
===========================================================

1. Install
----------

a. Installation from binary '.tar.gz' package

    # cp lcscan-0.3r3-i586.tar.gz /opt
    # cd /opt
    # tar -xzf lcscan-0.3r3-i586.tar.gz
    # cd lcscan
    # ./create_links

                or

    # tar -xzf lcscan-0.3r3-i586.tar.gz
    # cd lcscan
    # ./install

b. Installation from '.bin' package

    # ./lcscan-0.3r3-i586.bin

c. Installation from source package
     
    # tar -xzf lcscan-0.3r3.tar.gz
    # ./configure
    # make
    # make install

2. Uninstall
------------

a. If you installed it from binary '.tar.gz' package

    # /opt/lcscan/remove_links
    # rm -r /opt/lcscan/

            or

    # /opt/lcscan/uninstall

b. If you installed it from '.bin' package

    # /opt/lcscan/uninstall

c. If you installed it from source package:

    # make uninstall

